    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Doton)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 2 (Spell Level 1)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 5</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 15 | <b>Successes:</b> 2</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 3 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 15</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You press your hand to the earth and make the ground below the target area explode upward, dealing 2d6 earth damage. Prone targets take 50% extra damage. The ground underneath the target area must be firm or hard ground, such as densely packed dirt or stone.</p>\n\n\n\n",
